</div>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Brackern"> Brackern</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-1&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Surrounded around the <a href="/wiki/Shuriman_Continent" title="Shuriman Continent">Shuriman Continent</a> are several clans of <a href="/wiki/Brackern" title="Brackern">Brackern</a>, including clans in the Shuriman desert.
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Dormun"> Dormun</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-2&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div type="slideshow" widths="300" mode="slideshow" seq-no="0" id="slideshow-0" hash="33ecd670793118d62f686332e9da7b17" class="wikia-slideshow wikia-gallery floatright" data-hash="33ecd670793118d62f686332e9da7b17" data-crop="" data-seq-no="0"><div class="wikia-slideshow-wrapper" style="width: 300px"><div class="wikia-slideshow-images-wrapper"><div class="wikia-slideshow-prev-next"><a class="wikia-slideshow-prev" title="Previous photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a><a class="wikia-slideshow-next" title="Next photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a></div><ul class="wikia-slideshow-images neutral" style="height: 225px; width: 300px"><li class="wikia-slideshow-first-image"><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-0-0" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/4e/Shurima_Atop_The_Dormun_01.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917152707" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="150" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Shurima Atop The Dormun 01.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_Atop_The_Dormun_01.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Dormun 1" data-caption="Dormun 1" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">Dormun 1</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-0-1" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/58/Shurima_Atop_The_Dormun_02.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917152831" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="169" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Shurima Atop The Dormun 02.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_Atop_The_Dormun_02.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Dormun 2" data-caption="Dormun 2" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">Dormun 2</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-0-2" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/5c/Belzhun_Map_01.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/253?cb=20161202235810" class="thumbimage" width="253" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Belzhun Map 01.jpg" data-image-key="Belzhun_Map_01.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="A depiction of a Mwatis" data-caption="A depiction of a Mwatis" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">A depiction of a Mwatis</div></div></li></ul></div><div class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar"><div><span class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar-counter" data-counter="$1/3">1/3</span></div></div></div></div>
<p>The Dormun are gigantic, slow-moving creatures protected with large chitinous plates covering their body. In the harsh conditions of Shurima they have evolved to survive the perpetual drought by utilizing an unknown sense to locate hidden reservoirs of water. Incidentally, certain nomadic tribes have built themselves a permanent home upon the backs of these beasts where they clean the creature and hunt any airborne pests who venture near.
</p>
<h3><span id="Eka.27Sul"></span><span class="mw-headline" id="Eka'Sul"> Eka'Sul</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-3&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Desert goats that travel in herds.
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Mwatis"> Mwatis</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-4&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Mwatis are goatlike creatures with large plated casques on their heads. Mwati wool and plate are prised for felting and insulation.
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Kmiros"> Kmiros</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-5&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>Gigantic scarabs that roam in swarms, looking for unfortunate travelers to feed on. They seem to be common prey for <span class="inline-image character-background-icon label-after" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param=""><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Rammus" title="Rammus"><img alt="Rammus" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Rammus OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Rammus_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a1/Rammus_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160413190405" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Rammus" title="Rammus">Rammus</a></span></span>.
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Outerbeasts"> Outerbeasts</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-6&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<dl><dd><i><div class="dablink">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Void" class="mw-redirect" title="Void">Voidborn</a></div></i></dd></dl>
<div type="slideshow" widths="300" mode="slideshow" seq-no="1" id="slideshow-1" hash="a45b65a869be3476482a21e4a4fced77" class="wikia-slideshow wikia-gallery floatright" data-hash="a45b65a869be3476482a21e4a4fced77" data-crop="" data-seq-no="1"><div class="wikia-slideshow-wrapper" style="width: 300px"><div class="wikia-slideshow-images-wrapper"><div class="wikia-slideshow-prev-next"><a class="wikia-slideshow-prev" title="Previous photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a><a class="wikia-slideshow-next" title="Next photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a></div><ul class="wikia-slideshow-images neutral" style="height: 225px; width: 300px"><li class="wikia-slideshow-first-image"><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-1-0" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/Rek%27Sai_OriginalSkin.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20181021061755" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="177" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Rek&#39;Sai OriginalSkin.jpg" data-image-key="Rek%27Sai_OriginalSkin.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="A Xer&#39;Sai known as Rek&#39;Sai" data-caption="A Xer&#39;Sai known as " /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">A Xer'Sai known as <a href="/wiki/Rek%27Sai" title="Rek&#39;Sai">Rek'Sai</a></div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-1-1" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c1/Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_01.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/175?cb=20180307114241" class="thumbimage" width="175" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Kai&#39;Sa Breach concept 01.jpg" data-image-key="Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_01.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Kai&#39;Sa fighting Outerbeasts 1" data-caption=" fighting Outerbeasts 1" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption"><a href="/wiki/Kai%27Sa" title="Kai&#39;Sa">Kai'Sa</a> fighting Outerbeasts 1</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-1-2" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ea/Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_05.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/175?cb=20180307114843" class="thumbimage" width="175" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Kai&#39;Sa Breach concept 05.jpg" data-image-key="Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_05.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Kai&#39;Sa fighting Outerbeasts 2" data-caption=" fighting Outerbeasts 2" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption"><a href="/wiki/Kai%27Sa" title="Kai&#39;Sa">Kai'Sa</a> fighting Outerbeasts 2</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-1-3" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/94/Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_11.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/175?cb=20180307115219" class="thumbimage" width="175" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Kai&#39;Sa Breach concept 11.jpg" data-image-key="Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_11.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Kai&#39;Sa fighting Outerbeasts 3" data-caption=" fighting Outerbeasts 3" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption"><a href="/wiki/Kai%27Sa" title="Kai&#39;Sa">Kai'Sa</a> fighting Outerbeasts 3</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-1-4" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/35/Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_16.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/175?cb=20180307115437" class="thumbimage" width="175" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Kai&#39;Sa Breach concept 16.jpg" data-image-key="Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_16.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Kai&#39;Sa fighting Outerbeasts 4" data-caption=" fighting Outerbeasts 4" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption"><a href="/wiki/Kai%27Sa" title="Kai&#39;Sa">Kai'Sa</a> fighting Outerbeasts 4</div></div></li></ul></div><div class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar"><div><span class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar-counter" data-counter="$1/5">1/5</span></div></div></div></div>
<p>Beside the Xer'Sai, other creatures from the Void, referred to as 'outerbeasts', can be found in the desert.
</p>
<ul><li><b>Xer'Sai:</b> Creatures from the Void that plague the southern deserts. They are the size of big dogs on average, but can be smaller or much bigger. <span class="inline-image character-background-icon label-after" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param=""><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Rek%27Sai" title="Rek&#39;Sai"><img alt="Rek&#39;Sai" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Rek&#39;Sai OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Rek%27Sai_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0b/Rek%27Sai_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160526213622" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Rek%27Sai" title="Rek&#39;Sai">Rek'Sai</a></span></span>, as the queen, is by far the largest and most dangerous of her species. Xer'sai burst from their small burrows and ravage anything nearby, to the detriment of desert caravans. Once dead, the Xer'sai decompose at an abnormally rapid rate and become inedible.</li></ul>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Ralsiji"> Ralsiji</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-7&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div type="slideshow" widths="300" mode="slideshow" seq-no="2" id="slideshow-2" hash="5e9ab58a2549d5091817b438cd68d9da" class="wikia-slideshow wikia-gallery floatright" data-hash="5e9ab58a2549d5091817b438cd68d9da" data-crop="" data-seq-no="2"><div class="wikia-slideshow-wrapper" style="width: 300px"><div class="wikia-slideshow-images-wrapper"><div class="wikia-slideshow-prev-next"><a class="wikia-slideshow-prev" title="Previous photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a><a class="wikia-slideshow-next" title="Next photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a></div><ul class="wikia-slideshow-images neutral" style="height: 225px; width: 300px"><li class="wikia-slideshow-first-image"><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-2-0" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a3/Rek%27Sai_-_Scourge_of_the_Desert_05.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/156?cb=20141211015801" class="thumbimage" width="156" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Rek&#39;Sai - Scourge of the Desert 05.png" data-image-key="Rek%27Sai_-_Scourge_of_the_Desert_05.png" data-relevant="1" alt="A Ralsiji" data-caption="A Ralsiji" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">A Ralsiji</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-2-1" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/98/Rek%27Sai_-_Scourge_of_the_Desert_03.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/156?cb=20141211015800" class="thumbimage" width="156" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Rek&#39;Sai - Scourge of the Desert 03.png" data-image-key="Rek%27Sai_-_Scourge_of_the_Desert_03.png" data-relevant="1" alt="A Shuriman Camel 1" data-caption="A Shuriman Camel 1" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">A Shuriman Camel 1</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-2-2" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8b/Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_03.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/175?cb=20180307114533" class="thumbimage" width="175" height="225" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Kai&#39;Sa Breach concept 03.jpg" data-image-key="Kai%27Sa_Breach_concept_03.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="A Shuriman Camel 2" data-caption="A Shuriman Camel 2" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">A Shuriman Camel 2</div></div></li></ul></div><div class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar"><div><span class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar-counter" data-counter="$1/3">1/3</span></div></div></div></div>
<p>Large and aggressive minotaur-like creatures. They are humpbacked quadrupeds with long limbs and thick horns.
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Shuriman_Camel"> Shuriman Camel</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-8&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<p>A breed of camels native to the deserts of Shurima and are used by caravans as well as common folk as primary mode of  transportation. Despite being well-suited for lengthy travels in the desert landscape, they are still prey to a many predator such as the Xer'Sai.
</p>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Sandswimmers"> Sandswimmers</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-9&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<figure class="thumb tright show-info-icon" style="width: 300px"> 	<a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/47/Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180917152552" class="image"><img alt="Shurima Sandswimmers" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="300" height="98" class="thumbimage lazyload" data-image-name="Shurima Sandswimmers.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/47/Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917152552" /></a> 	<noscript><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/47/Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20180917152552" class="image"><img alt="Shurima Sandswimmers" src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/47/Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917152552" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="300" height="98" class="thumbimage" data-image-name="Shurima Sandswimmers.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/47/Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917152552" /></a></noscript> 	<figcaption class="thumbcaption"> 		 			<a href="/wiki/File:Shurima_Sandswimmers.jpg" class="info-icon"><svg><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-info-small"></use></svg></a> 		 		 		 			<p class="caption">Sandswimmers</p> 		 	</figcaption> </figure>
<p>Sandswimmers are massive quadrupedal creatures that traverse the Shuriman desert in cyclical patterns. They got their name due to their preferred method of travel. Their narrow bodies and webbed feet are perfectly design for swimming under the sand. They feed on bugs and other small creatures most desert beasts ignore. Scavengers will often memorize the predictable paths these creatures take, and jump onto their backs to ride as far as they wish.
</p>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
<p><br />
</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Skallashi"> Skallashi</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FShurima%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3DT-10&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div type="slideshow" widths="300" mode="slideshow" seq-no="3" id="slideshow-3" hash="b27e9ffe947b868af3a86512c901a4be" class="wikia-slideshow wikia-gallery floatright" data-hash="b27e9ffe947b868af3a86512c901a4be" data-crop="" data-seq-no="3"><div class="wikia-slideshow-wrapper" style="width: 300px"><div class="wikia-slideshow-images-wrapper"><div class="wikia-slideshow-prev-next"><a class="wikia-slideshow-prev" title="Previous photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a><a class="wikia-slideshow-next" title="Next photo"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-arrow-tiny"></use></svg></a></div><ul class="wikia-slideshow-images neutral" style="height: 225px; width: 300px"><li class="wikia-slideshow-first-image"><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-3-0" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a6/Shurima_Skallashi.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917152427" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="169" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Shurima Skallashi.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_Skallashi.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Skallashi" data-caption="Skallashi" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">Skallashi</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-3-1" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/f/fc/Shurima_The_Endless_Plain.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917151923" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="169" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Shurima The Endless Plain.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_The_Endless_Plain.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Skallashi in The Great Sai" data-caption="Skallashi in The Great Sai" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">Skallashi in The Great Sai</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-3-2" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8b/Shurima_Zoantha_Cascade_02.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917152313" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="169" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Shurima Zoantha Cascade 02.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_Zoantha_Cascade_02.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Skallashi at The Zoantha Cascade" data-caption="Skallashi at The Zoantha Cascade" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">Skallashi at The Zoantha Cascade</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-3-3" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/49/Shurima_The_Rebirth.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917145108" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="138" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Shurima The Rebirth.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_The_Rebirth.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Skallashi near The Sun Disc" data-caption="Skallashi near The Sun Disc" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">Skallashi near The Sun Disc</div></div></li><li><a class="image lightbox" title="Expand slideshow" id="slideshow-3-4" style="width: 220px"><img data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/15/Shurima_Market_Of_Illumination.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/300?cb=20180917150253" class="thumbimage" width="300" height="139" style="border: 0px;" data-image-name="Shurima Market Of Illumination.jpg" data-image-key="Shurima_Market_Of_Illumination.jpg" data-relevant="1" alt="Skallashi in Nashramae" data-caption="Skallashi in Nashramae" /></a><div class="wikia-slideshow-overlay"><div class="wikia-slideshow-image-caption">Skallashi in Nashramae</div></div></li></ul></div><div class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar"><div><span class="wikia-slideshow-toolbar-counter" data-counter="$1/5">1/5</span></div></div></div></div>
<p>The Skallashi are large quadrupedal herbivores. These hardy beasts of burden are common across Shurima, ideally suited to the harsh desert environment. Their key body feature is their long legs. Notoriously bad-tempered, they are nevertheless treated with great reverence. Their brown hides are often painted with sacred symbols of protection, and their horns hung with totems and charms. While these creatures are mostly used for travel and carrying heavy loads, on some larger skallashi people are able to built miniature rooms for more comfortable travel. To own one is often considered a sign of considerable prosperity.
</p>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
</div><div class="league-font" style="margin-bottom:1em; display:flow-root; position:relative; width:100%; max-width:min(1045px, calc(100% - 288px)); min-width:min(828px, 100%); min-height:180px; z-index:0; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto;"><sup style="position: absolute; top: 1em; right: 1em; z-index:2;text-shadow: 0 0 5px black;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ziggs_OriginalCentered.jpg" title="File:Ziggs OriginalCentered.jpg">Image</a></sup><div style="position:absolute; top:0px; right:0px; bottom:0px; left:0px; overflow:hidden;"><div style="position:absolute; left:0; top:0; width:100%; height:100%; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 100% 100% at 110% 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0), rgba(0,0,0,0) 60%, rgba(1,10,19,0.40) 100%, rgba(1,10,19,0.55) 120%, rgba(1,10,19,0.9) 150%); z-index:1"></div><div class="FullWidthImage fxaa" style="position:absolute; z-index:0; min-width:1000px; top:-65%;">
