</div><div style="width:100%; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 78px 3fr 1.4fr; row-gap: 0.5em;">
<div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;"> <div style="float:left;box-shadow:black 0 2px 5px 0;width:64px"><img alt="Bouncing Bomb" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="64" height="64" data-image-name="Ziggs Bouncing Bomb.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Bouncing_Bomb.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/85/Ziggs_Bouncing_Bomb.png/revision/latest?cb=20240813185932" class="lazyload" /></div></div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Ziggs</b> throws a bomb to the target location that bounces forward up to two times, with the distance traveled each time being based on how far it was originally thrown.</p></div>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2; display:contents">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p>The bomb explodes upon landing near an enemy, within terrain, or the final bounce, dealing <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to nearby enemies.</p></div>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse;"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;"><div style="padding: 0 7px"><div class="skill_leveling">
<dl class="skill-tabs"><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Magic Damage:</b></span></dt><dd>85 / 135 / 185 / 235 / 285 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 65% AP)</span></span></dd></dl></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><i>Bouncing Bomb will cast at max range if cast beyond that.</i></p></div>
</div>
</div></div></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div>
