<dd></dd></dl>
<ul><li>Base damage changed to 125 / 175 / 225 / 275 / 325.</li>
<li>AP ratio changed to <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">80% AP</span></span>.</li>
<li>Cooldown changed to 4 seconds at all ranks.<div style="clear:both"></div></li></ul>
