</aside>
</div><div style="width:100%; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 78px 3fr 1.4fr; row-gap: 0.5em;">
<div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;"> <div style="float:left;box-shadow:black 0 2px 5px 0;width:64px"><img alt="Satchel Charge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="64" height="64" data-image-name="Ziggs Satchel Charge.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b8/Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png/revision/latest?cb=20240813190009" class="lazyload" /></div></div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Ziggs</b> hurls a charge to the target location, remaining there for 4 seconds and granting <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">sight</a></span> of the area. <i>Satchel Charge</i> can be recast within the duration, and does so automatically afterwards. If recast while in flight, the charge will explode immediately upon landing.</p></div>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2; display:contents">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Recast:</b></span> <b>Ziggs</b> detonates the charge, causing it to explode to deal <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to nearby enemies and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Airborne"><a href="/wiki/Airborne" title="Airborne"><img alt="Airborne icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Airborne icon.png" data-image-key="Airborne_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d6/Airborne_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201223933" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Airborne" class="mw-redirect" title="Airborne">knock them back</a></span> up to 500 units away from the center of the explosion, though not through terrain. If this hits <b>Ziggs</b>, he will <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Dash"><a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash"><img alt="Dash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Dash.png" data-image-key="Dash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Dash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180514002826" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash">dash</a></span> up to 825 units away from the center.</p></div>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse;"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;"><div style="padding: 0 7px"><div class="skill_leveling">
<dl class="skill-tabs"><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Magic Damage:</b></span></dt><dd>70 / 105 / 140 / 175 / 210 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 50% AP)</span></span></dd></dl></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2; display:contents">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="inline-image label-after" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param=""><span style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><img alt="Turret Explosion:" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" title="Turret Explosion:" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Satchel Charge Turret Explosion Indicator.png" data-image-key="Satchel_Charge_Turret_Explosion_Indicator.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/2f/Satchel_Charge_Turret_Explosion_Indicator.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171130024522" class="lazyload" /></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><span class="template_sbc"><b>Turret Explosion:</b></span></span></span> The explosion also <a href="/wiki/Damage#Successful_ability_casts" title="Damage"><img alt="Successfully enhanced damage magic icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Successfully enhanced damage magic icon.png" data-image-key="Successfully_enhanced_damage_magic_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/f/ff/Successfully_enhanced_damage_magic_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240624101228" class="lazyload" /></a> <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="Cosmetic critical strike"><span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Execute"><a href="/wiki/Kill#Execute" title="Kill"><img alt="Death from Below" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Pyke Death from Below.png" data-image-key="Pyke_Death_from_Below.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/19/Pyke_Death_from_Below.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813145427" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Kill#Execute" title="Kill">executes</a></span></span> enemy <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Turrets"><a href="/wiki/Turret" title="Turret"><img alt="Turret icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Turret icon.png" data-image-key="Turret_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/82/Turret_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180701054101" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Turret" title="Turret">turrets</a></span> within that are below a <span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed with Comeuppance (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal"><b>maximum</b> health</span></span> threshold.</p></div>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse;"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;"><div style="padding: 0 7px"><div class="skill_leveling">
<dl class="skill-tabs"><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Demolition Threshold:</b></span></dt><dd><span class="ll-item navbox">Champions killed with Comeuppance (R)</span><span><span style="color: #1F995C; white-space:normal">25 / 27.<small>5</small> / 30 / 32.<small>5</small> / 35% of turret's <b>maximum</b> health</span></span></dd></dl></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><i><b>Ziggs</b> does not <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Dash"><a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash"><img alt="Dash" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Dash.png" data-image-key="Dash.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/Dash.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180514002826" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Dash" title="Dash">dash</a></span> if he is <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Immobilize"><a href="/wiki/Crowd_control#Immobilizing" title="Crowd control"><img alt="Stun icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Stun icon.png" data-image-key="Stun_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9d/Stun_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201223940" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Crowd_control#Immobilizing" title="Crowd control">immobilized</a></span> or <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Ground"><a href="/wiki/Ground" title="Ground"><img alt="Grounded icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Grounded icon.png" data-image-key="Grounded_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/26/Grounded_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160509000039" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Ground" class="mw-redirect" title="Ground">grounded</a></span>. He can cast any of his abilities during the dash.</i></p></div>
</div>
</div></div></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div>
