</section>
</aside>

<ul><li>The initial cast counts as an ability activation for the purposes of on-cast effects such as <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Spellblade"><a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Spellblade" title="Named item effect"><img alt="Sheen item" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sheen item.png" data-image-key="Sheen_item.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c6/Sheen_item.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20201118210052" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Named_item_effect#Spellblade" title="Named item effect">Spellblade</a></span> and triggering <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Kassadin" data-ability="Force Pulse" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Kassadin/LoL#Force_Pulse" title="Force Pulse&#39;s"><img alt="Force Pulse&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Kassadin Force Pulse.png" data-image-key="Kassadin_Force_Pulse.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/22/Kassadin_Force_Pulse.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813002424" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Kassadin/LoL#Force_Pulse" title="Kassadin/LoL">Force Pulse's</a></span></span> passive.
<ul><li>Detonating the ability manually does not.</li></ul></li>
<li>Deals <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Area damage"><a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage"><img alt="Death Lotus" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Katarina Death Lotus.png" data-image-key="Katarina_Death_Lotus.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/77/Katarina_Death_Lotus.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813002735" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage">area damage</a></span> to non-turrets and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Raw damage"><a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage"><img alt="Fear Beyond Death 2" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Urgot Fear Beyond Death 2.png" data-image-key="Urgot_Fear_Beyond_Death_2.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e0/Urgot_Fear_Beyond_Death_2.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813173421" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Damage" title="Damage">raw damage</a></span> to turrets.</li>
<li><i>Satchel Charge's</i> distance increases with proximity to the charge, resulting in being knocked straight up when aligned directly on top of it.</li>
<li><b>Ziggs</b> will not <i>dash</i> from <i>Satchel Charge's</i> detonation while <span class="inline-image label-after spell-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-spell="Teleport" data-game="lol"><span class="border icon-20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Teleport" title="Teleporting"><img alt="Teleporting" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Teleport.png" data-image-key="Teleport.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e8/Teleport.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180514003653" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Teleport" title="Teleport">Teleporting</a></span></span> but he will while <span class="inline-image label-after spell-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-spell="Recall" data-game="lol"><span class="border icon-20" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Recall" title="Recalling"><img alt="Recalling" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Recall.png" data-image-key="Recall.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/4/43/Recall.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171227214733" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Recall" title="Recall">Recalling</a></span></span>.</li></ul>
<div style="clear:both"></div>
</div><p class="mw-empty-elt"></p></div><div class="wds-tab__content"><p class="mw-empty-elt"> 
</p><div style="display:none;"><b>Map-Specific Differences</b><br /></div>
<div style="padding:0.5em 1em;">&#32;
<dl><dt><span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Howling abyss"><a href="/wiki/Howling_Abyss_(League_of_Legends)" title="Howling Abyss (League of Legends)"><img alt="Howling Abyss icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Howling Abyss icon.png" data-image-key="Howling_Abyss_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/02/Howling_Abyss_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171101151627" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Howling_Abyss_(League_of_Legends)" title="Howling Abyss (League of Legends)">Howling Abyss</a></span> differences <sup><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/Template:Map_changes/data/aram?action=edit">edit</a></sup></dt>
