<div class="skill skill_e" style="padding: 1em; margin-top: 1em; font-size:14px;box-shadow:black 0 2px 5px 0;color:#c8c4bd; border:#525244 solid 1px; background:#061e36 no-repeat right top; overflow:hidden; position:relative; z-index: 100;">
<div class="skill_header skill_wrapper"><span class="plainlinks"><a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/Template:Data_Ziggs/Hexplosive_Minefield?action=edit"><span class="button" title="Click here to edit this ability." style="float:right; text-align:center; border-radius: 2px; position:absolute; right:13px; z-index:5"><b>Edit</b></span></a></span><div class="ability-info-container"><div class="champion-ability&#95;_header"><h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Hexplosive_Minefield">Hexplosive Minefield</span></h3>

