</div><div style="width:100%; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 78px 3fr 1.4fr; row-gap: 0.5em;">
<div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;"> <div style="float:left;box-shadow:black 0 2px 5px 0;width:64px"><img alt="Hexplosive Minefield" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="64" height="64" data-image-name="Ziggs Hexplosive Minefield.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Hexplosive_Minefield.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/76/Ziggs_Hexplosive_Minefield.png/revision/latest?cb=20240813185942" class="lazyload" /></div></div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Ziggs</b> scatters a cluster of 11 proximity mines over the target location that grant <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">sight</a></span> of the area for 2 seconds, <span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="travel time of the mines spreading out plus a brief delay">arming after 0.<small>5</small> seconds</span> and lasting for up to 10 seconds.</p></div>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;">&#32;</div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2; display:contents">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p>Each mine within the area explodes upon contact with terrain or an enemy, dealing <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> and <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Slow"><a href="/wiki/Slow" title="Slow"><img alt="Slow icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Slow icon.png" data-image-key="Slow_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/78/Slow_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201224744" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Slow" class="mw-redirect" title="Slow">slowing</a></span> them for 1.<small>5</small> seconds, as well as granting <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">sight</a></span> of the area around the explosion for 2 seconds. An enemy takes 40% damage from subsequent mines.</p></div>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse;"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;"><div style="padding: 0 7px"><div class="skill_leveling">
<dl class="skill-tabs"><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Magic Damage per Mine:</b></span></dt><dd>30 / 70 / 110 / 150 / 190 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 30% AP)</span></span></dd><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Reduced Damage per Mine:</b></span></dt><dd>12 / 28 / 44 / 60 / 76 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 12% AP)</span></span></dd><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Maximum Total Magic Damage:</b></span></dt><dd>150 / 350 / 550 / 750 / 950 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 150% AP)</span></span></dd></dl>
<dl class="skill-tabs"><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Slow:</b></span></dt><dd>10 / 20 / 30 / 40 / 50%</dd></dl></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</div>
</div></div></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div>
