</div><div style="width:100%; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 78px 3fr 1.4fr; row-gap: 0.5em;">
<div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;"> <div style="float:left;box-shadow:black 0 2px 5px 0;width:64px"><img alt="Mega Inferno Bomb" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="64" height="64" data-image-name="Ziggs Mega Inferno Bomb.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Mega_Inferno_Bomb.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d4/Ziggs_Mega_Inferno_Bomb.png/revision/latest?cb=20240813190001" class="lazyload" /></div></div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2;">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p><span class="template_sbc"><b>Active:</b></span> <b>Ziggs</b> catapults the <i>Mega Inferno Bomb</i> to the target location, granting <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Sight"><a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight"><img alt="Sight icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Sight icon.png" data-image-key="Sight_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Sight_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20130928145820" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Sight" title="Sight">sight</a></span> within a 600 radius around its destination for 4 seconds.</p></div>
</div><div style="text-align:center; padding:7px; vertical-align:top;"><div style="float:left;box-shadow:black 0 2px 5px 0;width:64px"><img alt="Mega Inferno Bomb Minimap" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="64" height="64" data-image-name="Mega Inferno Bomb Minimap.png" data-image-key="Mega_Inferno_Bomb_Minimap.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e2/Mega_Inferno_Bomb_Minimap.png/revision/latest?cb=20150701035801" class="lazyload" /></div></div>
<div style="grid-column-end: span 2; display:contents">
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 0 0 0 7px;"><p>The bomb explodes upon arrival to deal <span class="ll-item navbox">Damage mitigated with Shifting Sands (E)</span><span><span style="color: #00B0F0; white-space:normal">magic damage</span></span> to enemies hit, increased by 50% against those in the epicenter.</p></div>
<table style="border-collapse: collapse;"><tbody><tr><td style="vertical-align:top;"><div style="padding: 0 7px"><div class="skill_leveling">
<dl class="skill-tabs"><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Magic Damage:</b></span></dt><dd>200 / 300 / 400 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 73.<small>3<span style="text-decoration: overline;">3</span></small>% AP)</span></span></dd><dt><span class="template_lc"><b>Increased Damage:</b></span></dt><dd>300 / 450 / 600 <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">(+ 110% AP)</span></span></dd></dl></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>
</div>
<div style="vertical-align:top; padding: 5.2px 7px 0 10em; font-style:italic; font-size:larger; grid-column-end: span 3;"><span><audio hidden="" class="ext-audiobutton" data-volume="0.7" preload="none"><source src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/73/Ziggs_Original_R_2.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20230105070909" type="application/ogg" /><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/73/Ziggs_Original_R_2.ogg/revision/latest?cb=20230105070909">Link</a></audio><a class="ext-audiobutton" data-state="play" title="Play/Pause">▶️</a></span><sup><a href="/wiki/File:Ziggs_Original_R_2.ogg" title="File:Ziggs Original R 2.ogg">&#160;&#160;</a></sup> <i>"I bring the Big One!"</i></div></div></div></div></div><div style="clear:both"></div>
