ic.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/e9/Ziggs_LaIlusi%C3%B3nCircle.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/48?cb=20230913013027" class="lazyload" /></span></span></div><div class="skinviewer-tab-container"><div class="skinviewer-tab-content skinviewer-active-tab" style="display:block;" data-id="item-1"><div class="skinviewer-tab-skin" style="position:relative;font-family:BeaufortLoL;"><div class="FullWidthImage" style="max-width:1240px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;"><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/93/Ziggs_OriginalSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20181021104706" class="image"><img alt="Ziggs OriginalSkin" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1215" height="717" data-image-name="Ziggs OriginalSkin.jpg" data-image-key="Ziggs_OriginalSkin.jpg" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/93/Ziggs_OriginalSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20181021104706" class="lazyload" /></a></div><div style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);border-radius:6px 6px 0 0;line-height:24px;bottom:0;height:24px;right:0;left:0;font-size:20px;justify-content:space-between;border-right:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);border-left:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);position:absolute;display:flex;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);z-index:100;align-items:flex-end;"><div style="color:#d3c7aa;flex:4 1 0px;text-align:center;font-weight:700;"><span title="0">Original</span></div><div style="text-align:center;flex:1 1 0px;"><span class="plainlinks"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.modelviewer.lol/model-viewer?id=115000"><span class="button" title="View in 3D" style="text-align:center; border-radius: 2px;"><b>View in 3D</b></span></a></span></div><div class="skinviewer-price" title="This skin is available to purchase with RP from the store."><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/00/RP_icon.png/revision/latest?cb=20241201161019" class="image" title="RP"><img alt="RP" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="RP icon.png" data-image-key="RP_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/00/RP_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20241201161019" class="lazyload" /></a> 880</div><div style="text-align:center;padding-right:2px;color:#c9aa71;flex:1 1 0px;font-size:smaller;">01.02.2012</div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);padding:15px;font-family:BeaufortLoL;font-size:14px;"><div class="skinviewer-info-lore"><div style="line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center; font-size: 15px;">With a love of big bombs and short fuses, the yordle Ziggs is an explosive force of nature. As an inventor’s assistant in Piltover, he was bored by his predictable life and befriended a mad, blue-haired bomber named Jinx. After a wild night on the town, Ziggs took her advice and moved to Zaun, where he now explores his fascinations more freely, terrorizing the chem-barons and regular citizens alike in his never ending quest to blow stuff up.</div><div><div class="center"><div class="floatnone"><img alt="Separator" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="7" data-image-name="Separator.png" data-image-key="Separator.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/10/Separator.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20180110165522" class="lazyload" /></div></div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-kleine-bilder" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;"><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Actor" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlh