="chroma-caption" title="21">Sweet Tooth</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-tab-content" style="display:none;" data-id="item-10"><div class="skinviewer-tab-skin" style="position:relative;font-family:BeaufortLoL;"><div class="FullWidthImage" style="max-width:1240px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;"><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d2/Ziggs_HextechSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200818223424" class="image"><img alt="Ziggs HextechSkin" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1215" height="717" data-image-name="Ziggs HextechSkin.jpg" data-image-key="Ziggs_HextechSkin.jpg" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d2/Ziggs_HextechSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200818223424" class="lazyload" /></a></div><div style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);border-radius:6px 6px 0 0;line-height:24px;bottom:0;height:24px;right:0;left:0;font-size:20px;justify-content:space-between;border-right:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);border-left:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);position:absolute;display:flex;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);z-index:100;align-items:flex-end;"><div style="color:#d3c7aa;flex:4 1 0px;text-align:center;font-weight:700;"><span title="23">Hextech</span></div><div style="text-align:center;flex:1 1 0px;"><span class="plainlinks"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.modelviewer.lol/model-viewer?id=115023"><span class="button" title="View in 3D" style="text-align:center; border-radius: 2px;"><b>View in 3D</b></span></a></span></div><div class="skinviewer-price" style="flex 1 1 0px; text-align:center;" title="125 Mythic Essence">Special</div><div style="text-align:center;padding-right:2px;color:#c9aa71;flex:1 1 0px;font-size:smaller;">03.09.2020</div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);padding:15px;font-family:BeaufortLoL;font-size:14px;"><div class="skinviewer-info-lore"><div style="line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center; font-size: 15px;">Famed inventor of Tocker, Ziggs is a savant to some, to others a maniac. All can agree that no matter the consequences, Ziggs seems to enjoy his experiments—especially the subsequent explosions. What is perhaps most miraculous of all is how he and Tocker have survived so many blasts over the years.</div><div><div class="center"><div class="floatnone"><img alt="Separator" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="7" data-image-name="Separator.png" data-image-key="Separator.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/10/Separator.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20180110165522" class="lazyload" /></div></div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-kleine-bilder" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;"><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Actor" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Actor.png" data-image-key="Actor.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a9/Actor.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180529054842" class="lazyload" />Alessandro Juliani</div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Artist" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Artist.png" data-image-key="Artist.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a5/Artist.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180528201217" class="lazyload" />Horace 'Hozure' Hsu</div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Set piece" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Set piece.png" data-image-key="Set_piece.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/5d/Set_piece.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180529081027" class="lazyload" /> <a href="/wiki/Hextech_(Universe)" title="Hextech (Universe)">Hextech</a></div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Loot eligible" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Loot eligible.png" data-image-key="Loot_eligible.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ed/Loot_eligible.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20190905165101" class="lazyload" /> Loot eligible</div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-grosse-bilder" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;padding-top:5px;"><div style="padding:0 1em; text-align:center;"><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon"><img alt="New effects" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" data-image-name="New effects.png" data-image-key="New_effects.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/54/New_effects.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/50?cb=20180330200341" class="lazyload" /></div><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon">New SFX/VFX</div></div><div style="padding:0 1em; text-align:center;"><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon"><img alt="New animations" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="50" height="50" data-image-name="New animations.png" data-image-key="New_animations.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/5/55/New_animations.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/50?cb=20180330200340" class="lazyload" /></div><div class="skin-viewer-text-icon">New Animations/Recall</div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-variantof" style="text-align:center;"></div></div><div class="skinviewer-tab-chroma"></div></div><div class="skinviewer-tab-content" style="display:none;" data-id="item-11"><div class="skinviewer-tab-skin" style="position:relative;font-family:BeaufortLoL;"><div class="FullWidthImage" style="max-width:1240px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;"><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/39/Ziggs_BZZZiggsSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20220215234830" class="image"><img alt="Ziggs BZZZiggsSkin" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1215" height="717" data-image-name="Ziggs BZZZiggsSkin.jpg" data-image-key="Ziggs_BZZZiggsSkin.jpg" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/39/Ziggs_BZZZiggsSkin.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20220215234830" class="lazyload" /></a></div><div style="background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);border-radius:6px 6px 0 0;line-height:24px;bottom:0;height:24px;right:0;left:0;font-size:20px;justify-content:space-between;border-right:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);border-left:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);position:absolute;display:flex;border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.25);z-index:100;align-items:flex-end;"><div style="color:#d3c7aa;flex:4 1 0px;text-align:center;font-weight:700;"><span title="24">BZZZiggs</span></div><div style="text-align:center;flex:1 1 0px;"><span class="plainlinks"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.modelviewer.lol/model-viewer?id=115024"><span class="button" title="View in 3D" style="text-align:center; border-radius: 2px;"><b>View in 3D</b></span></a></span></div><div class="skinviewer-price" title="This skin is available to purchase with RP from the store."><a href="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/00/RP_icon.png/revision/latest?cb=20241201161019" class="image" title="RP"><img alt="RP" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="RP icon.png" data-image-key="RP_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/00/RP_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20241201161019" class="lazyload" /></a> 1350</div><div style="text-align:center;padding-right:2px;color:#c9aa71;flex:1 1 0px;font-size:smaller;">03.03.2022</div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info" style="background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);padding:15px;font-family:BeaufortLoL;font-size:14px;"><div class="skinviewer-info-lore"><div style="line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center; font-size: 15px;">According to all known laws of apiculture, bees shouldn't be given explosives. Hey! Put that bouncing bomb down, bee!</div><div><div class="center"><div class="floatnone"><img alt="Separator" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="7" data-image-name="Separator.png" data-image-key="Separator.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/10/Separator.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20180110165522" class="lazyload" /></div></div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-kleine-bilder" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;"><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Actor" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Act