chaos. Whether it's lobbing Ardor to weaken a building pylon or lighting a destructive thought in someone's mind like a brushfire, there is no reason behind his madness, only whatever catches his cool blue eyes.</div><div><div class="center"><div class="floatnone"><img alt="Separator" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="400" height="7" data-image-name="Separator.png" data-image-key="Separator.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/10/Separator.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20180110165522" class="lazyload" /></div></div></div></div><div class="skinviewer-info-kleine-bilder" style="display:flex;justify-content:center;"><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Actor" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Actor.png" data-image-key="Actor.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a9/Actor.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180529054842" class="lazyload" />Alessandro Juliani</div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Artist" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Artist.png" data-image-key="Artist.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/a/a5/Artist.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20180528201217" class="lazyload" />Yuyu Wong, Kudos&#160;Productions</div><div style="padding-right:1em; text-align:center;"><img alt="Set piece" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Set piece