<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Patch_history">Patch history</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FZiggs%2FLoL%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<dl><dd><i>For the expanded patch notes, see <a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL/Patch_history" title="Ziggs/LoL/Patch history">here</a>.</i></dd></dl>
<div style="overflow:auto; max-height:330px; width:100%; margin:3px 0; border:1px solid #AAAAAA; padding:0 0.5em 0 0.5em; box-sizing:border-box; -moz-box-sizing:border-box; -moz-border-radius-topleft:0.5em; background:transparent; border-radius:4px;">
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V14.18" title="V14.18">V14.18</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Short Fuse" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Short_Fuse" title="Short Fuse"><img alt="Short Fuse" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Short Fuse.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Short_Fuse.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8e/Ziggs_Short_Fuse.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813190021" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Short_Fuse" title="Ziggs/LoL">Short Fuse</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Structure damage reduced to 175% from 250%.
<ul><li>Base damage against structures reduced to <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-displayformula="35 + 7 per level up to 6, then + 14 per level up to level 12, then + 21 per level" data-bot_values="35;42;49;56;63;70;84;98;112;126;140;154;175;196;217;238;259;280" data-top_values="">35 &#8722; 280 (based on level)</span> from <span class="pp-tooltip" style="position:relative; border-bottom:1px dotted; cursor:help;" data-displayformula="50 + 10 per level up to 6, then + 20 per level up to level 12, then + 30 per level" data-bot_values="50;60;70;80;90;100;120;140;160;180;200;220;250;280;310;340;370;400" data-top_values="">50 &#8722; 400 (based on level)</span>.</li>
<li>AP ratio against structures reduced to <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">87.<small>5</small>% AP</span></span> from <span class="ll-item navbox">Multiple champions hit with Between Worlds (R)</span><span><span style="color: #7A6DFF; white-space:normal">125% AP</span></span>.</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V14.3" title="V14.3">V14.3</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Base armor increased to 21 from 18.</li>
<li>Armor growth increased to 4.<small>7</small> from 4.<small>5</small>.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Satchel Charge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Satchel_Charge" title="Satchel Charge"><img alt="Satchel Charge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Satchel Charge.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b8/Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813190009" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Satchel_Charge" title="Ziggs/LoL">Satchel Charge</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Cooldown reduced to 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12 seconds from 24 / 21 / 18 / 15 / 12.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V14.2" title="V14.2">V14.2</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Satchel Charge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Satchel_Charge" title="Satchel Charge"><img alt="Satchel Charge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Satchel Charge.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b8/Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813190009" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Satchel_Charge" title="Ziggs/LoL">Satchel Charge</a></span></span>
<ul><li><span class="template_sbc"><b>Bug Fix:</b></span> Cast is no longer locked out while he is <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Ground"><a href="/wiki/Ground" title="Ground"><img alt="Grounded icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Grounded icon.png" data-image-key="Grounded_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/26/Grounded_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160509000039" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Ground" class="mw-redirect" title="Ground">grounded</a></span> or <span class="glossary" style="white-space:pre; position:relative;" data-game="lol" data-tip="Root"><a href="/wiki/Root" title="Root"><img alt="Root icon" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" data-image-name="Root icon.png" data-image-key="Root_icon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/6/6b/Root_icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171201224302" class="lazyload" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Root" class="mw-redirect" title="Root">rooted</a></span>.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V13.23" title="V13.23">V13.23</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Base attack damage increased to 55 from 54.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Bouncing Bomb" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Bouncing_Bomb" title="Bouncing Bomb"><img alt="Bouncing Bomb" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Bouncing Bomb.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Bouncing_Bomb.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/85/Ziggs_Bouncing_Bomb.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185932" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Bouncing_Bomb" title="Ziggs/LoL">Bouncing Bomb</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Base damage reduced to 85 / 135 / 185 / 235 / 285 from 95 / 145 / 195 / 245 / 295.</li></ul></li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Satchel Charge" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Satchel_Charge" title="Satchel Charge"><img alt="Satchel Charge" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Satchel Charge.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/b8/Ziggs_Satchel_Charge.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813190009" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Satchel_Charge" title="Ziggs/LoL">Satchel Charge</a></span></span>
<ul><li>Cooldown increased to 24 / 21 / 18 / 15 / 12 seconds from 20 / 18 / 16 / 14 / 12.</li>
<li>Mana cost increased to 80 from 65.</li></ul></li></ul>
<dl><dt><a href="/wiki/V13.22" title="V13.22">V13.22</a></dt></dl>
<ul><li>Stats
<ul><li>Base armor reduced to 18 from 22.</li>
<li>Attack windup reduced to 20% from 20.<small>833333</small>%.</li></ul></li></ul>
