<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Trivia">Trivia</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a title="Sign in to edit" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor" data-tracking-label="log-in-edit-section" data-action="edit-section" href="https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fleagueoflegends.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FZiggs%2FLoL%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D4&amp;uselang=en" data-testid="log-in-edit-section"><svg class="wds-icon wds-icon-tiny"><use xlink:href="#wds-icons-pencil-tiny"></use></svg></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li>Ziggs is the first (so far only) champion to have all his abilities (except innates) be the same type (ground-targeted area of effect).</li>
<li>Ziggs is one of the few champions that can apply crowd control on themselves (the others being <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Caitlyn" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Caitlyn/LoL" title="Caitlyn"><img alt="Caitlyn" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Caitlyn OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Caitlyn_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/3/35/Caitlyn_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20230215152459" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Caitlyn/LoL" title="Caitlyn/LoL">Caitlyn</a></span></span>, <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Lissandra" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Lissandra/LoL" title="Lissandra"><img alt="Lissandra" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Lissandra OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Lissandra_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/6/6c/Lissandra_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160526213305" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Lissandra/LoL" title="Lissandra/LoL">Lissandra</a></span></span>, <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Rumble" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Rumble/LoL" title="Rumble"><img alt="Rumble" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Rumble OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Rumble_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/be/Rumble_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402220909" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Rumble/LoL" title="Rumble/LoL">Rumble</a></span></span>, <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Sion" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Sion/LoL" title="Sion"><img alt="Sion" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Sion OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Sion_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ea/Sion_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402221054" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Sion/LoL" title="Sion/LoL">Sion</a></span></span>, <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Varus" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Varus/LoL" title="Varus"><img alt="Varus" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Varus OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Varus_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/9c/Varus_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20171215205843" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Varus/LoL" title="Varus/LoL">Varus</a></span></span>, <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Vi" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Vi/LoL" title="Vi"><img alt="Vi" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Vi OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Vi_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/e/ec/Vi_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160526214220" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Vi/LoL" title="Vi/LoL">Vi</a></span></span> and <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Xerath" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Xerath/LoL" title="Xerath"><img alt="Xerath" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Xerath OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Xerath_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cf/Xerath_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402222520" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Xerath/LoL" title="Xerath/LoL">Xerath</a></span></span>).</li>
<li>Ziggs' dance references <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KVuIBpJ6B4E">'Midget Superstar'.</a>
<ul><li>A side-by-side comparison can be seen <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MohuzSxA46E">here.</a></li></ul></li>
<li>Ziggs was a <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://twitter.com/RiotZiegler/status/165616431315169281">nickname</a> for Rioter <a href="/wiki/Joe_%27Hephastopheles%27_Ziegler" title="Joe &#39;Hephastopheles&#39; Ziegler">Joe 'Hephastopheles' Ziegler</a>.</li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Heimerdinger" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Heimerdinger/LoL" title="Heimerdinger"><img alt="Heimerdinger" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Heimerdinger OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Heimerdinger_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/9/97/Heimerdinger_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402220126" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Heimerdinger/LoL" title="Heimerdinger/LoL">Heimerdinger</a></span></span> reveals that Ziggs's full name is <i>Zigmund</i>, from <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Germanic_languages">Proto-Germanic</a> <i>*segiz</i> "victory" &amp; <i>*mundō</i> "<span class="basic-tooltip" style="border-bottom:1px dotted gray;cursor:help;" title="original meaning is hand">protection</span>";<sup id="cite_ref-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-2">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> the latter element is shared with <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Dr. Mundo" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Dr._Mundo/LoL" title="Dr. Mundo"><img alt="Dr" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Dr. Mundo OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Dr._Mundo_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/c3/Dr._Mundo_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20210526185145" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Dr._Mundo/LoL" title="Dr. Mundo/LoL">Dr. Mundo</a></span></span>.</li>
<li>Ziggs and <span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Nautilus" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Nautilus/LoL" title="Nautilus"><img alt="Nautilus" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Nautilus OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Nautilus_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d2/Nautilus_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160526213414" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Nautilus/LoL" title="Nautilus/LoL">Nautilus</a></span></span> were first conceived as '<span class="inline-image unit-icon label-after" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param=""><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ivan" title="Ivan"><img alt="Ivan" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="IvanSquare.png" data-image-key="IvanSquare.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/71/IvanSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160219180119" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ivan" class="mw-redirect" title="Ivan">Ivan</a></span></span> the Mad Bomber'.</li>
<li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Hexplosive Minefield" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Hexplosive_Minefield" title="Hexplosive Minefield"><img alt="Hexplosive Minefield" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Hexplosive Minefield.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Hexplosive_Minefield.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/76/Ziggs_Hexplosive_Minefield.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813185942" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Hexplosive_Minefield" title="Ziggs/LoL">Hexplosive Minefield</a></span></span> was conceived as Ziggs' ultimate (was later replaced by <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Mega Inferno Bomb" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Mega_Inferno_Bomb" title="Mega Inferno Bomb"><img alt="Mega Inferno Bomb" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Mega Inferno Bomb.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Mega_Inferno_Bomb.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d4/Ziggs_Mega_Inferno_Bomb.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813190001" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Mega_Inferno_Bomb" title="Ziggs/LoL">Mega Inferno Bomb</a></span></span>)
<ul><li><span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Mega Inferno Bomb" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Mega_Inferno_Bomb" title="Mega Inferno Bomb&#39;s"><img alt="Mega Inferno Bomb&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Mega Inferno Bomb.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Mega_Inferno_Bomb.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/d4/Ziggs_Mega_Inferno_Bomb.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813190001" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Mega_Inferno_Bomb" title="Ziggs/LoL">Mega Inferno Bomb's</a></span></span> icon references a <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/nuclear_weapon">nuclear weapon</a>.</li></ul></li>
<li>Ziggs seems to be the mascot for <a href="/wiki/Featured_game_mode" title="Featured game mode">featured game modes</a>.
<ul><li>This is evident from his likeness being used on <span class="inline-image label-after" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param=""><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><img alt="numerous" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" title="numerous" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Mirror Mode profileicon.png" data-image-key="Mirror_Mode_profileicon.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/0/0e/Mirror_Mode_profileicon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170517181936" /></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/One_for_All" title="One for All">numerous</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param=""><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><img alt="summoner" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" title="summoner" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Doom Icon of Doom profileicon.png" data-image-key="Doom_Icon_of_Doom_profileicon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/1/16/Doom_Icon_of_Doom_profileicon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170504215259" /></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Doom_Bots" title="Doom Bots">summoner</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param=""><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><img alt="icons" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" title="icons" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Nemesis Draft profileicon.png" data-image-key="Nemesis_Draft_profileicon.png" data-relevant="1" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/c/cd/Nemesis_Draft_profileicon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20170504221513" /></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Nemesis_Draft" title="Nemesis Draft">icons</a></span></span> that represent or commemorate them, as well as having his <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Sneakpeek_Ziggs.jpg">teaser picture</a> be the base for the promotional art <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Hexakill_mode.jpg">for</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:The_Doom_Bots_of_Doom_mode_old.jpg">a</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:FGM_Nemesis_Draft.jpg">lot</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:FGM_Nexus_Siege.png">of</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:One_for_All_art.png">these</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Ultra_Rapid_Fire_art.png">game</a> <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener" class="text" href="https://leagueoflegends.fandom.com/wiki/File:Legend_of_the_Poro_King.png">modes</a>.</li></ul></li>
<li>A prop of Ziggs' <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Ziggs" data-ability="Short Fuse" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Short_Fuse" title="Hexplosive Bomb"><img alt="Hexplosive Bomb" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Ziggs Short Fuse.png" data-image-key="Ziggs_Short_Fuse.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/8/8e/Ziggs_Short_Fuse.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813190021" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Ziggs/LoL#Short_Fuse" title="Ziggs/LoL">Hexplosive Bomb</a></span></span> was crafted in an episode of YouTube series <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLUUGFk1wE5OHBnwRKxqDWTL3DgrfoiRmr">DIY Prop Shop</a>.
<ul><li>This video can be viewed <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3I6MK1SV1Lk">here</a>.
<ul><li>There are also videos where the following are crafted:
<ul><li><span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Diana" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Diana/LoL" title="Diana&#39;s"><img alt="Diana&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Diana OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Diana_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/da/Diana_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20160526212149" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Diana/LoL" title="Diana/LoL">Diana's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Diana" data-ability="Moonfall" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Diana/LoL#Moonfall" title="Crescent Moonblade"><img alt="Crescent Moonblade" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Diana Moonfall.png" data-image-key="Diana_Moonfall.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/29/Diana_Moonfall.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240810180333" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Diana/LoL#Moonfall" title="Diana/LoL">Crescent Moonblade</a></span></span></span> (<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kz-0nfkVegg">functional</a>)</li>
<li><span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Katarina" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Katarina/LoL" title="Katarina&#39;s"><img alt="Katarina&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Katarina OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Katarina_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/7/7e/Katarina_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402220331" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Katarina/LoL" title="Katarina/LoL">Katarina's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Katarina" data-ability="Preparation" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Katarina/LoL#Preparation" title="Daggers"><img alt="Daggers" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Katarina Preparation.png" data-image-key="Katarina_Preparation.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/2/28/Katarina_Preparation.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20240813002745" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Katarina/LoL#Preparation" title="Katarina/LoL">Daggers</a></span></span></span> (<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lq-h3KkF_bY">functional</a>)</li>
<li><span class="champion-ability-icon"><span class="inline-image label-after champion-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Leona" data-skin="Original" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL" title="Leona&#39;s"><img alt="Leona&#39;s" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Leona OriginalSquare.png" data-image-key="Leona_OriginalSquare.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/b/ba/Leona_OriginalSquare.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20150402220518" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL" title="Leona/LoL">Leona's</a></span></span> <span class="inline-image label-after ability-icon" style="display:inline;white-space:pre;" data-param="" data-champion="Leona" data-ability="Zenith Blade" data-game="lol"><span class="border" style="display:inline-block;position:relative;" data-width="20"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL#Zenith_Blade" title="Zenith Blade"><img alt="Zenith Blade" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" class="thumbborder lazyload" data-image-name="Leona Zenith Blade.png" data-image-key="Leona_Zenith_Blade.png" data-relevant="0" data-src="https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/leagueoflegends/images/d/db/Leona_Zenith_Blade.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/20?cb=20230830010729" /></a></span> <span style="white-space:normal;"><a href="/wiki/Leona/LoL#Zenith_Blade" title="Leona/LoL">Zenith Blade</a></span></span></span> (<a target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" class="external text" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yEwne-IEG9s">functional</a>)</li>
